the X.25 compatible LAPB procedures as specified in @cite{ISO/IEC 7776}
described in reference @ref{ISO7776,,ISO7776}.
This driver, in combination with the @file{x25} multiplexing driver, provides
X.25 over LAPB as described in reference @ref{ISO8208,,ISO8208}.

The @file{lapb} driver provides a @cite{Data Link Provider Interface} as its
upper multiplex service interface, as described in @ref{DLPI,,DLPI}.

The @file{lapb} driver is documented in the @manref{lapb(4)} manual page.

